v1.0.6

Balance Changes:
+ Cookie Upgrader buffed to 1.5 multi, range 5m - 15m
+ Sugar Churner buffed to range 10m - 30m
+ Gumball Enchanter buffed to range 0 - 25m
+ Azure Scanner conveyor speed decreased from 12 -> 6 
+ Slushie Dropper now has neon ore (was supposed to)

+ Chartreuse Collider now works *after* the Ore Wash, not before
+ Netrozite Mine is now correctly given as an achievement. All players that already earned the achievement will have this in their inventory

Bug Fixes:
+ Fixed the pop-up for crates not showing up on console
+ Fixed a bug where gamepass gifting was incorrectly preventing players from receiving gifts
+ Cookie Upgrader can now actually touch ore
+ Cookie Upgrader will now flash when ore is invalid

+ Secrets unboxed stat now increments for Corium Mine
+ Secret badge is now awarded to Corium Mine owners
